  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink235-kilavi">uṭaṉpōkku nērvittapiṉpu talaimakaṉ uṭaṉkoṇṭupōvāṉ iṭaiyāmattu vantuḻit talaimakaṭkut tōḻi colliyatu. </p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> What the confidante said to the heroine
          when, after the elopement had been agreed upon,
          the hero who was to take [her] along
          came at midnight.          
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink235">
<l>kaiyuṟa vīḻnta maiyil vāṉamo</l>
<l>ṭaritu kātalarp poḻutē yataṉāṟ</l>
<l>ṟeriyiḻai teḷirppa muyaṅkip</l>
<l>piriyala meṉkamō veḻukamō teyyō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>This time is rare for lovers,</l>
        <l rend="indent">[accompanied] by skies [now] cloudless,</l>
        <l rend="indent2">[from which the rains] have [already] fallen,</l>
        <l>so that [the skies] have [done their] work/</l>
        <l>so that the hands [of the people] experience [the rains].</l>
        <l rend="space">Therefore, shall we,</l>
        <l>having embraced him so that our choice jewels shine,</l>
        <l>say, “We shall never separate”?</l>
        <l>Shall we rise?</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
